          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-Admin-1623406804158-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-Admin-1623406804158-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-Admin-1623406804158-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle and peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, tear your <strong>'Nduja </strong>into the pan<strong> </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596538905399-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596538905399-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596538905399-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596538905399-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1596538905399-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the 'Nduja is softening, add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti</strong> and <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the spaghetti and Tenderstem broccoli are cooked with a slight bite, then drain, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Return the <strong>drained spaghetti</strong> and <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to the pot with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and stir it all together</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596538922942-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596538922942-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596538922942-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596538922942-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1596538922942-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the 'Nduja has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>with 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until thickened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1596538937890-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1596538937890-x400.jpg",
